text.tspan: This thesis contributes to the field of Embodied Artificial Intelligence.
We strive to create intelligent agents able to perceive the world,
temporal relationships, and act to reach a pre
defined goal. We distinguish three problems we need to address. First,

Then, we consider a first simple form of interaction with an unknown
